The paper focuses on improving visual place recognition using convolutional neural networks, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves selecting a subset of feature maps within a layer, which is a technique related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE.
